short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enable extended tools for camunda cockpit.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Camunda Tools is a simple and effective tool designed to facilitate the movement of process instances within the Camunda BPM platform. This application streamlines the process of reorganizing workflows, providing a straightforward solution to optimize process instance management.
